articles.author: Hilary Whiteman
articles.title: Millions of Australian children just lost access to social media. What’s happening and will it work? - CNN
articles.description: Children across Australia will wake up on Wednesday with no access to their social media accounts under a world-first ban designed to shelter those under 16 from addictive algorithms, online predators, and digital bullies.
